<title>USA: AMEX closing averages.</title>
<headline>AMEX closing averages.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed lower in heavy trading.</p>
<p>The Amex Composite index closed at 623.27, down 5.03.</p>
<p>The average price per share fell $0.11.</p>
<p>Decliners beat advancers 288 to 256.</p>
<p>Preliminary volume was 28,757,775 compared with 26,949,010 on Thursday.</p>
<p>(Prices official as of 1630 EST/2130 GMT)</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1830))</p>
